column3: Large, rolling terrains of grasses, flowers and herbs.

Temperate,broadleaf forest with mid weather and healthy trees
Swiftly-flowing freshwater streams,Rocky and sandy beaches play home,
Vast open ocean, with sunlit waters, and deep frigid sea floor and icy seas
Little to no light penetrates into dark, damp caverns and winding caves
Defined by the humans that live in them and the environments that they create.
